    <item>
      <title>尽管存在危险信号，Polymarket 对华尔街选举“游戏计划”的影响力仍在不断增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们普遍怀疑投资者应该在多大程度上相信加密货币预测市场 Polymarket 发出的信号，但华尔街仍密切关注该平台上的押注，该平台显示唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选的可能性很高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/polymarket-s-influence-on-wall-street-s-game-plan-grows-despite-red-flags</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 16:16:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维勒鲁瓦表示，欧洲的未来由各国政府而非欧洲央行决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/villeroy-says-governments-not-the-ecb-are-defining-europe-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行正面临新的经济现实，各国政府也应该这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/villeroy-says-governments-not-the-ecb-are-defining-europe-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 15:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯战略轰炸机访问南非被推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/russian-strategic-bomber-visit-to-south-africa-is-postponed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯原计划向比勒陀利亚派遣两架战略轰炸机，以展示两国国防合作，但由于遭到南非联合政府一位主要成员的批评，这一计划被推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/russian-strategic-bomber-visit-to-south-africa-is-postponed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 15:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥市长提议提高房产税，违背竞选承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/chicago-mayor-proposes-property-tax-hike-to-solve-budget-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊提议将房产税提高 3 亿美元，这违背了竞选承诺，即帮助弥补明年近 10 亿美元的预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/chicago-mayor-proposes-property-tax-hike-to-solve-budget-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 15:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监督机构称加拿大必须加倍国防开支才能达到北约目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/canada-must-double-annual-defense-spending-to-meet-nato-target-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大预算监督机构表示，加拿大必须将国防开支增加近一倍，才能兑现到 2032 年达到北约提出的国防开支占国内生产总值 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/canada-must-double-annual-defense-spending-to-meet-nato-target-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 15:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西政府接近达成削减支出协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/brazil-s-government-moves-closer-to-agreeing-on-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 赢得了政府支出削减最大批评者之一的支持，接近批准旨在缓解投资者对该国财政前景担忧的紧缩计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/brazil-s-government-moves-closer-to-agreeing-on-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:31:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对俄罗斯战争机器供应商实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-sanctions-hundreds-of-targets-supplying-russia-s-war-machine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正在对印度、中国和土耳其的近 400 名个人和公司实施制裁，以打击一个庞大的网络，该网络在俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰近三年后仍帮助俄罗斯的战争机器保持运转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-sanctions-hundreds-of-targets-supplying-russia-s-war-machine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:30:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯提高英国税收，借款投资选举后预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/reeves-raises-uk-taxes-by-40-billion-in-labour-s-first-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯宣布增加 400 亿英镑（518 亿美元）的税收 — — 这是几十年来最高的 — — 并且增加了借贷，这两项重大举措旨在履行工党“重建”英国的承诺，但预计对经济增长和公共支出的提振作用仍然很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/reeves-raises-uk-taxes-by-40-billion-in-labour-s-first-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 12:54:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州传唤总统讨论选举舞弊调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/georgia-summons-president-for-questions-in-election-fraud-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚检察机关已对该国议会选举中的舞弊指控展开调查，并表示计划对总统萨洛梅·祖拉比奇维利进行质询，解释其关于选举结果被操纵的说法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/georgia-summons-president-for-questions-in-election-fraud-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 10:11:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列讨论以美国为首的新协议以结束真主党冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/israel-eyes-deal-to-end-lebanon-combat-after-weakening-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在评估真主党武装分子的火箭弹库已基本耗尽或被摧毁后，以色列正在考虑接受由美国主导的一项协议，以结束黎巴嫩冲突并将真主党武装分子撤出以色列边境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/israel-eyes-deal-to-end-lebanon-combat-after-weakening-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:51:48 GMT</pubDate>
